isis.stitle: TSI 99-12-10 - Performance Specifications for Model Year 1999 International® DT 466E and International 530 Engine Applications

subjectgroup.subject: Performance Specifications for Model Year 1999 International® DT 466E and International 530 Engine Applications

geninfo.para: Engine Performance Specifications are being released to service for the International DT 466E and International 530 Engine Applications.

note.para:
Emission label
on engine correctly identifies the Engine Model Year and Horsepower Rating.
